{"tid":856388,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★夜市：蘋果公司跌逾1.5%，騰訊ADR低見279港元，恐連挫10日。","createTime":"2018-10-10T14:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T16:43:49.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"703fc99ef22c3282b76f4efdf33c517a6e7612ff","tid":856388,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:27:33.000Z","msg":"科技股遭到拋售，納指瀉122點或1.59%，至7,615點。美國科技股中，蘋果公司跌逾1.5%，特斯拉跌約4%，亞馬遜跌逾2%，Facebook跌逾1%。騰訊ADR弱勢未改，低見279港元，恐連挫10日。<br />\n<br />\n周三美國10年期國債孳息率攀升至3.24%，接近2011年以來的最高水平。最近美股交易受到了美國國債收益率上漲與加息的影響。二者均表明長期延續的超低利率時期行將結束，美股市場可能已進入危機後的新階段。<br />\n<br />\n港股期指夜市在美股開市後走勢急轉直下，目前報25,903點，跌262點，低水290點。恒指ADR跌200點至26,024點。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181010/bkn-20181010213638390-1010_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181010%2Fbkn-20181010213638390-1010_00842_001.html&d=LyEjm9il6BC0muFEPB%2B4C2Mi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=ac634227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181010/bkn-20181010213638390-1010_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"46ef885e92f259098694f6362e800581cc374f8d","tid":856388,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50721516b930d43dc5d23924f7e99d541c90080f","tid":856388,"uid":56097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be559edae3460f85639e414161010a1a4dba3ed8","tid":856388,"uid":103759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn